{"pin":"BH00238","subcodes":[{"code":"BH00238","anchor":"","title":"Lawh-i-Dunya (Tablet of the World)","first_line":"Praise and thanksgiving beseem the Lord of manifest dominion Who hath adorned the mighty prison… The betterment of the world can be accomplished","first_line_orig":"حمد و ثنا سلطان مبین را لایق و سزاست که سجن متین را بحضور حضرت علی قبل اکبر  ","language":"5","word_count":"2590","subjects":"@lists; enumerations of Baha'i principles, @walking the spiritual path; spiritual wayfaring; the virtuous life, @serving humanity; working for progress, betterment of the world, @love and unity, @power and sovereignty of God; omnipotence of God, @House of Justice, @unity in diversity, @call to action","notes":" \u003ca href=\"https://d9263461.github.io/cl/Baha'i/Others/ROB/V4/Contents.html\"\u003eROB4.329 et al\u003c/a\u003e,  \u003ca href=\"http://bluefin.live/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/BKOG.pdf#page=23\"\u003eBKOG.382\u003c/a\u003e,  \u003ca href=\"http://bluefin.live/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/BKOG.pdf#page=23\"\u003eBKOG.399\u003c/a\u003e,  \u003ca href=\"http://bluefin.live/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/BKOG.pdf#page=23\"\u003eBKOG.410\u003c/a\u003e,  \u003ca href=\"http://bluefin.live/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/BKOG.pdf#page=23\"\u003eBKOG.454\u003c/a\u003e,  \u003ca href=\"https://bahai-library.com/bahailib/1504.pdf#page=143\"\u003eMMAH.131\u003c/a\u003e,  \u003ca href=\"https://reference.bahai.org/fa/t/o/GS/gs-168.html\"\u003eGSH.168\u003c/a\u003e,  \u003ca href=\"http://web.archive.org/web/20070930181707/http://bahai-library.com/resources/leiden.list/leiden.list.html#83\"\u003eLL#083\u003c/a\u003e","full_text_parts":["Light and glory, greeting and praise be upon the Hands of His Cause, through whom the light of fortitude hath shone forth and the truth hath been established that the authority to choose rests with God, the Powerful, the Mighty, the Unconstrained, through whom the ocean of bounty hath surged and the fragrance of the gracious favors of God, the Lord of mankind, hath been diffused.  We beseech Him—exalted is He—to shield them through the power of His hosts, to protect them through the potency of His dominion, and to aid them through His indomitable strength which prevaileth over all created things.  Sovereignty is God's, the Creator of the heavens and the Lord of the Kingdom of Names.\n\n* Tablets of Bahá’u’lláh, Lawh-i-Dunyá (Tablet of the World)"],"translations":[],"writing_refs":[{"type":"tablets","type_name":"Tablets of Bahá'u'lláh","language":"fr","lang_name":"French"},{"type":"tablets","type_name":"Tablets of Bahá'u'lláh","language":"it","lang_name":"Italian"},{"type":"tablets","type_name":"Tablets of Bahá'u'lláh","language":"nl","lang_name":"Dutch"},{"type":"tablets","type_name":"Tablets of Bahá'u'lláh","language":"sv","lang_name":"Swedish"},{"type":"tablets","type_name":"Tablets of Bahá'u'lláh","language":"tvl","lang_name":"Tuvalu"},{"type":"tablets","type_name":"Tablets of Bahá'u'lláh","language":"ar","lang_name":"Arabic"},{"type":"tablets","type_name":"Tablets of Bahá'u'lláh","language":"es","lang_name":"Spanish"},{"type":"tablets","type_name":"Tablets of Bahá'u'lláh","language":"tl","lang_name":"Tagalog"},{"type":"tablets","type_name":"Tablets of Bahá'u'lláh","language":"de","lang_name":"German"},{"type":"tablets","type_name":"Tablets of Bahá'u'lláh","language":"pl","lang_name":"Polish"},{"type":"tablets","type_name":"Tablets of Bahá'u'lláh","language":"en","lang_name":"English"},{"type":"tablets","type_name":"Tablets of Bahá'u'lláh","language":"fa","lang_name":"Persian"},{"type":"tablets","type_name":"Tablets of Bahá'u'lláh","language":"lv","lang_name":"Latvian"},{"type":"tablets","type_name":"Tablets of Bahá'u'lláh","language":"pt","lang_name":"Portuguese"},{"type":"tablets","type_name":"Tablets of Bahá'u'lláh","language":"ro","lang_name":"Romanian"},{"type":"tablets","type_name":"Tablets of Bahá'u'lláh","language":"zh-Hans","lang_name":"Simplified Chinese"}]},{"code":"BH00238HAN","anchor":"han"